how to build
=========
call 'make' in the terminal

how to run
========
call 'make' in the terminal. Then a wakefields and energy spreads with different parameters are calculated. This can be changed in 'task.cpp / make()'.

how to look at the data
================
the data are written to a file. The files can be plotted by gnuplot 'filename.dat'.
In the header of the file information to the parameter is written. 
